\", \"score\": 0.9850078774770851, \"rank\": 0.013979870599394756, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Flying from Cork Airport since 2018, the French airline provides a direct, daily service to Paris Charles de Gaulle airport from March 31st to October 29th, 2024.\", \"from\": 428, \"to\": 590, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 469, \"end\": 475, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9850078774770851, \"rank\": 0.013979870599394756, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 520, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Paris Charles de Gaulle airport\", \"types\": [\"Q1248784\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_de_Gaulle_Airport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The service provides excellent access to the French capital, along with onward connectivity to 187 onward destinations across the wider Air France worldwide network.\", \"from\": 592, \"to\": 757, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 637, \"end\": 643, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9850078774770851, \"rank\": 0.013979870599394756, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}, {\"begin\": 728, \"end\": 738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.6796661985535856e-49, \"text\": \"Air France\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q46970\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Air_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Air France will operat